abstract: >
  This repository provides a formal mathematical functional-necessity theorem for the Layer-0 minimum of Large Language Models, a declared obligation-graph enumeration over the six-role set, and public witness tables separating the LLM root from Transformer, Dense, MoE, SSM, recurrent, and frontier implementation branches.
